<%=fontTextXXL%>Instructions</font>
<%=hr%>
<p><b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'><a name=enter>To enter Success Criteria</a></span></b>:</p>
<ol start=1 type=1>
  <li><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Click on “Tools” on the Staff 
    Site Main Menu Bar.</span></li>
</ol>
<ol start=2 type=1>
  <li><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Click on the “Infobase” icon in 
    the “Ministry and Team Tracking” section.</span></li>
</ol>
<ol start=3 type=1>
  <li><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>In the upper right hand corner 
    of the InfoBase home page is a campus search mechanism. It says, “List Campuses 
    with the ‘name’ =,” and then there is an empty box. Type in your campus name 
    (do not use abbreviations) in the box and click on SEARCH.</span></li>
</ol>
<ol start=4 type=1>
  <li>A list of campuses will appear. Choose yours and click on it.  Do <u>not</u> 
    click on the Team; Click on the <u>campus</u> itself.</li><BR><br>
  <li>Scroll down the page to the box that talks about your strategy (example 
    below).  You should see a green <img width=24 height=25
     src="./help_enter_success_criteria_files/image002.gif" v:shapes="_x0000_i1025"> 
    in the box.  Click on it.</li>
</ol>
<p><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:Arial'> <center><img width=437 height=71 src="./help_enter_success_criteria_files/image004.jpg"> 
  </center></span></p>
<ol start=6 type=1>
  <li>You will now see a row of red X’s and green checks.  The red “x” indicates 
    that the  Success Criteria for that week have yet to be entered.  Click the 
    red “x” under the week for which you would like to enter Success Criteria. 
    <b>If you would like to skip steps 1 -5 in the future, you can bookmark this 
    page and a link to this page will now appear on both your Staff Site Homepage 
    and the &quot;Success Criteria&quot; Page</b>.  To learn how to bookmark click 
    <a href="/help/help_infobase.jsp#bmcampus">here</a>.</li>
</ol>
<p><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'> <center><img width=217 height=70
src="./help_enter_success_criteria_files/image006.jpg" v:shapes="_x0000_i1027"> 
  </center></span></p>
<ol start=7 type=1>
  <li><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>You are now on the form where 
    you actually enter your Success Criteria for the week. Fill in the fields 
    on the form.</span></li>
</ol> 
<p><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Important Note: </span></p>
<ol start=7 type=1>
  <ul type=disc>
    <li><span
      style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>The numbers that you enter under 
      “This Week’s Criteria” will be added to the numbers in any report that includes 
      this week in its date range. </span></li>
    <li>“Campus Demographics” is a snapshot.  It is important to include these 
      numbers each week that you fill out Success Criteria.  These numbers are 
      <u>NOT</u> carried over from week to week. For any field left blank a zero 
      is recorded.  When Success Criteria reports are compiled for your campus, 
      the reports will take the most recently entered &quot;campus demographics&quot; 
      numbers within the specified date range of the report.  This is why it is 
      important to fill these fields in every time success criteria is entered.</li>
  </ul>
</ol>
<p><ol start=8 type=1>
<li>When you have finished filling out the form, click on  “submit.”  You 
  will then be taken to the confirmation page.</p>
</li></ol>
